title: Aerofoil Profile Paper Plane NO OMNIWING
description:
* INFO *
New generation of paper planes! With wings shaped like the wings of a real airplane, the profile paper plane has the ability to fly a much longer distance than a usual paperplane. Developed with the help of CAD Software by german engineer.
The wings of this paper airplane have an aerofoil like a real airplane: The wing has a Profile Shape. This Profile leads to awesome in-flight characteristics. There is no Paper Airplane which has nearly the same glide ratio like the "profile paper plane". In this Video you will learn how to Make This awesome Paperplane.
